'''Hon-khek''' (yu tsiang '''Gong-dung hon-khek''') heh yit chung tsin-thung [[Haak-gaa]] [[hi-khek]], yu heh [[Haak-gaa-ngin]] ui khon geh ngi-sut-phin chung chi yit. Gaai khek chung chi-yew liu-hang yi [[Kóng-tûng|Gong-dung]] [[東|dung-phu]] geh Haak-gaa thi-khi. Heung Hon-khek gong geh faa heh leui-tsi [[Chung-yen]] geh [[Phu-thung-faa]].
